Pushpa 2 - The Rule - Written and Directed by Sukumar. Produced by Naveen Yerneni and Y. snippet.title: FAMILY AUR SHAADI KI SHOPPING..!!
snippet.description:
Let's take you men's wear shopping for the festive wedding season at the most happening place in Hyderabad in the Banjara Hills at the Asuka Store

Walk in and experience the medley of heritage and old world charm with the modern, just like their collection, and exult in the ritual of fine dressing, an experience that's gonna leave you savouring in the fragrance of tommorow!

The design house hails from Delhi where they've been manufacturers of men's wear garments for over 35 years. From ceremonial suits for festive occasions, Sherwanis for Weddings, ornate Bandhgalas, Kurtas, indowestern attire in wide range of hues, fabrics, embroidery, and matching shoes and accesories, it's a one stop shop for men who like to dress the best! 

Shop Ethnic and Western Men's wear at Asuka Store 
Visit : Banjara Hills, Road No. 2, Hyderabad

Instagram : @ asukacouture

For Business Inquiry : hyderabaddiaries@yahoo.com

Second Channel:
Hyderabad Diaries Vlogs: www.youtube.com/hyderabaddiariesvlogs

Presenting "Lifemates - a story of Husband & Wife by Take A Break. This Series is based on the characters Prashant & Sayali from our shorts channel "Shorts Break".

Lifemates is a story of every married couple out there. Prashant & Sayali navigate their day to day life as a couple, facing the perks and challenges of marriage, and figuring out what it takes to keep yourself committed to the bond.

Lifemates Episode 1 is coming to you on 16th April, only on Take A Break Youtube Channel.

snippet.title: Dino James - Boyfriend Part 1 ft. Benafsha Soonawalla | Music Prod By @BluishMusic & Sez On The beat
snippet.description:
Boyfriend is a song where Dino James portrays the insecurities and toxicity that an individual can go through in a relationship and the trauma that follows if they let themselves fall deep into the dark hole of insecurities. An uncomfortable truth that a lot of people face. Through this song, Dino James has a strong message ‚ÄúIf this is what people face, best for both parties to walk away. Toxicity and trauma is never okay‚Äù

Finally, we enjoy the puri recipe with our favorite mutton curry!

The taste is, Crispy and Yummy!

snippet.description:

Well, he is here now ready to rule your hearts once again after all the love that has been showered on him. The wait is finally over, now get ready to Meet Bhaijaan in Kisi Ka Bhai Kisi Ki Jaan where the family drama will be max with a tadka of romance and action.

Hello Foodies!
In this video, we'll show you how to make a delicious and spicy Bangalore special Kara Bath recipe, along with a Neer Chutney that perfectly complements the dish. Kara Bath is a popular breakfast dish in Bangalore, made with semolina, vegetables, and a blend of aromatic spices. We'll show you how to make this flavorful dish step-by-step and also share some tips and tricks to make it even more delicious. And to balance out the spiciness of the Kara Bath, we'll also be making a simple and spicy Neer Chutney, made with coconut, green chilies, and coriander. This chutney is the perfect accompaniment to the Kara Bath and will leave you feeling satisfied. So, follow the steps shown in this video to learn how to make this classic Bangalore breakfast dish with a twist!

snippet.title: NEW! Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah - Ep 3740 - 8 Apr 2023 - Teaser
snippet.description:
Episode 3740: Lucky Draw Ka Din
--------------------------------------------------------
Popatlal warns that he would take severe action against Ramsang Corporation if no one from Gokuldham wins the prize. Popatlal is notified by Jetha that Ramsang is among the most well-known businesses in the industry and that they will not put up with such unfounded accusations. Before the lucky draw is broadcasted, Bhide makes the request that everyone observe decorum and silence so that everyone can watch the program in peace. Finally, the lucky draw starts and everyone starts staring at the television in awe. Residents of Gokuldham are impatiently awaiting the announcement of the winner. Who will take home the car in this jackpot? To find out, watch the episode!

              Raashi hamesha dikhati hai neecha Gopi ko aur karti hai uske liye mushkilen taiyaar. Par Gopi ka haath thama Kokilaben ne aur banaya ussey hoshiyaar. Iss saas-bahu ki jodi ne apne pyaar, dulaar aur balidaan se bandhe rakha hai Modi parivaar ko.

snippet.title: Legacy - Amit Bhadana (Official Music Video) | Bintu Pabra | KP Kundu | The Kidd | Vaksh Vimal |
snippet.description:
This song is the fourth single by Amit Bhadana. After Parichay, Aatmvishvas and Father Saab now i bring you Legacy. Through Legacy I am trying to convey a simple message - If you choose not to be the part of the rat race, stay firm on your resolve and never compromise on your principles you can achieve anything under the sun. This song showcase Three major chunks of My life, one in my village where 5 years of my life were spent, second where i spent 20 years in Delhi and my present life where i am fullfilling all my dreams and taking care of my family .You will get a glimpse of my journey from village to city, days of extreme poverty in a new location and my struggle. With hardwork i overcame every hardship and created a better life for myself and my loved ones. I believe that this is just the beginning. I dream of a much better future and need every bit of your support to make it a reality. With quality content, creativity and vision I want to add value to my viewers lives. In the past 6 years I have learnt alot and taught alot (you know it better) and I wish to keep entertaining everyone for the rest of my life. I want to create a legacy that goes on from genaration to generation Please watch this song and don‚Äôt forget to share it with your family and friends. Legacy. Love.

#‡§§‡§æ‡§∞‡§ï‡§Æ‡•á‡§π‡§§‡§æ‡§ï‡§æ‡§â‡§≤‡•ç‡§ü‡§æ‡§ö‡§∂‡•ç‡§Æ‡§æ

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
--------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired from the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story evolves around happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. The show predominantly - Promoolves around 'Jethalaal' (Dilip Joshi) who is an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta' (Sailesh Lodha), is his neighbor. 'Jethalaal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' (Disha Wakani) and a mischievous son 'Tapu' (Bhavya Gandhi). Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalaal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises. Lost hopes of being heard by his son pushes Jethalaal' to call his father 'Champaklal' (Amit Bhatt) from the village. This was his great idea of leashing some control over the mischievous Tapu. The opposite happens and the grandfather joins hands with the grandson to make life a roller coaster troublesome ride for Jethalaal.

Click to watch all the Weekly Reliv episodes: https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PL6Rtnh6YJK7aq_DUPLxBkU49WEPPcecgS

snippet.description:
Thanks for watching Har Pal Geo. Please click here https://bit.ly/3rCBCYN to Subscribe and hit the bell icon to enjoy Top Pakistani Dramas and satisfy all your entertainment needs. Do you know Har Pal Geo is now available in the US? Share the News. Spread the word.

Qalandar Episode 55 - [Eng Sub] - Muneeb Butt - Komal Meer - Ali Abbas - 9th April 2023 - HAR PAL GEO

Qalandar is a story of a girl‚Äôs firm belief in her God and His decisions while the rest of the world continues to hurt, defame and challenge her.

Dur-e-Adan is a young and innocent girl who has grown up under the care of her uncle and aunt. Despite being an orphan at an early age, Dur-e-Adan doesn‚Äôt complain about her challenges and difficulties.

On the contrary, Tabriz is a handsome young man who aspires to achieve great things in life. Living in the same locality, Tabriz‚Äôs parents find Dur-e-Adan suitable for him as a life partner. However, Tabriz‚Äôs life takes a surprising turn when Sumbul hailing from a wealthy family falls in love with him. In efforts to secure his future financially, Tabriz forgets the gift that he has been bestowed in the form of Dur-e-Adan for this world and hereafter. Soon, Tabriz‚Äôs half-heartedness and conflicting loyalties in the form of greed begins to reflect in his relationship with Dur-e-Adan.

Amidst all the atrocities faced by Dur-e-Adan will she continue to be patient with those around her? Will Tabriz realize the respect and love that Dur-e-Adan deserves or will he continue to hurt her? Will Tabriz be able to mend his relationship with Dur-e-Adan?

Soon their lives go through a series of emotional sufferings and misunderstandings where it becomes difficult for them to coexist. Despite their hatred towards each other, will Meerab and Murtasim accept their true feelings or will the dynamics of ego and self-respect force them to stay apart?

snippet.title: Lagan Tumse Laga Baithe | Bholenath Song | Jo Hoga Dekha Jayga | New Song 2023 | Shekhar Jaiswal
snippet.description:
Shekhar Jaiswal Presents New Bholenath Song "Lagan Tumse Laga Baithe" 

Shekhar Jaiswal Instagram - https://www.instagram.com/theshekharjaiswal

Singer, Composer, Lyrics - Shekhar Jaiswal (9719998366)
Music - GW Music Studio Rudrapur (Saif)
Cast - Shekhar Jaiswal & Vishal Gangwar Team
Direction & Scripted By - Soumya Jaiswal
Cinematography - Lucky Hundal
Location - Rudrapur (Uttarakhand)
Edited By - Shekhar Jaiswal

Other Channel - https://youtube.com/c/ShekharJaiswalComedy

Booking - 9719998366, 7451940400
Shekharredifmail@gmail.com


Lyrics -
-----------------------------------------

Lagan tumse lga baithe jo hoga dekha jayga
Tume apna bana baithe jo hoga dekha jayga..

Kaise kese du meri dua beasar ho gai
Jab bhi roya mere shambhunath ko khrab ho gai..
Nzar bholenath ki padi is kdar humpar
Nazarandaz walo ki bhi nzar ho gai..
Tume dil se laga baithe
Jo hoga dekha jayga
Lagan tumse lga baithe jo hoga dekha jayga

Nam mera hua baba tu krne wala hai
Jo bhi sankat tha mere sar me tune tala hai
Tera hi naam le lekr me sare kam kru
Kehte hai log banda kismat wala hai
Teri galiyo me aa baithe
Jo hoga dekha jayga..
Lagan tumse lga baithe jo hoga dekha jayga

snippet.description:
Thanks for watching Har Pal Geo. Please click here https://bit.ly/3rCBCYN to Subscribe and hit the bell icon to enjoy Top Pakistani Dramas and satisfy all your entertainment needs. Do you know Har Pal Geo is now available in the US? Share the News. Spread the word.

Qalandar Episode 56 Teaser - 9th April 2023 - HAR PAL GEO

Qalandar is a story of a girl‚Äôs firm belief in her God and His decisions while the rest of the world continues to hurt, defame and challenge her.

Dur-e-Adan is a young and innocent girl who has grown up under the care of her uncle and aunt. Despite being an orphan at an early age, Dur-e-Adan doesn‚Äôt complain about her challenges and difficulties.

On the contrary, Tabriz is a handsome young man who aspires to achieve great things in life. Living in the same locality, Tabriz‚Äôs parents find Dur-e-Adan suitable for him as a life partner. However, Tabriz‚Äôs life takes a surprising turn when Sumbul hailing from a wealthy family falls in love with him. In efforts to secure his future financially, Tabriz forgets the gift that he has been bestowed in the form of Dur-e-Adan for this world and hereafter. Soon, Tabriz‚Äôs half-heartedness and conflicting loyalties in the form of greed begins to reflect in his relationship with Dur-e-Adan.

Amidst all the atrocities faced by Dur-e-Adan will she continue to be patient with those around her? Will Tabriz realize the respect and love that Dur-e-Adan deserves or will he continue to hurt her? Will Tabriz be able to mend his relationship with Dur-e-Adan?

Produced By: Abdullah Kadwani & Asad Qureshi
Head of Project: Mikaal Zulfiqar

----------------------
The Gada family finally reaches home and they are extremely exhausted from the journey. The next morning Daya calls her mother to verify what she told her. After the phone call, she laughs out loud and Jetha curiously wants to know the reason behind it. Stay tuned to know what happens further!

Show Name ‚Äì Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #‡§§‡§æ‡§∞‡§ï‡§Æ‡•á‡§π‡§§‡§æ‡§ï‡§æ‡§â‡§≤‡•ç‡§ü‡§æ‡§ö‡§∂‡•ç‡§Æ‡§æ  #sonypal

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
----------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story evolves around happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. The show predominantly revolves around 'Jethalaal' (Dilip Joshi), an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta' (Sailesh Lodha), is his neighbor. 'Jethalaal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' (Disha Wakani) and a mischievous son 'Tapu' (Raj Anankat). Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalaal' to reform 'Tapu' or be prepared to leave the premises.

Ethirneechal is a popular Tamil serial that revolves around the life of Janani, who is always driven to succeed by her father. While waiting for Thapki and Bani, Aryan learns that Thapki and Bani have met with an accident! Shocked and devastated, the Pandey family at once rush to the hospital. Will Thapki and Bani survive this traumatic accident?

The bright and beautiful Thapki is pretty much perfect... except for one minor flaw - she stammers. But that doesn't hold her back. All she needs is an encouraging pat on the back,a 'thapki', which soon becomes her name. Over the course of the show, Thapki falls in love with Dhruv, but is duped into getting married to his brother, Bihaan. snippet.description:
Click here to Subscribe to Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah Official Channel: https://www.youtube.com/taarakmehtakaooltahchashmah?sub_confirmation=1 

Click here to watch all your favorite Episode videos: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=gqFEadNxmd8&list=PLPbh-P_C0BzRYOkpGxKL-6QmvYSL_ZuCu 

We bring to you the best videos from your favorite show Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah. So, get your daily dose of laughter with Jethalal, Taarak Mehta, Daya, Champaklal and their neighbors in Gokuldham Society.

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
--------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired from the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story revolves around daily happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. The show predominantly - revolves around 'Jethalal' (Dilip Joshi) who is an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta' (Shailesh Lodha), is his neighbor. 'Jethalal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' (Disha Wakani) and a mischievous son 'Tapu' (Bhavya Gandhi / Raj Anadkat). Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises. Lost hopes of being heard by his son push Jethalaal' to call his father 'Champaklal' (Amit Bhatt) from the village. This was his great idea of leashing some control over the mischievous Tapu. The opposite happens and the grandfather joins hands with the grandson to make life a roller coaster troublesome ride for Jethalal.

---------

Lyrics:-

Mere Rashk E Qamar
TuNe Pehli Nazar
Jab Nazar Se Milayi Maza Aa gaya

Barq Si Gir Gayi
Kaam Hee Kar Gayi
Aag Aisee Lagaayi Maza Aa gaya

Jaam Mein Ghoul Kar Hun Kee Mastiyaan
Chaandni Muskurai Maza Aagaya
Chaand Ke Sa'ay Mein Ay Mere Saaqiya
TuNe Aisee Pilaayi Maza Aagaya

Nasha Sheeshe Mein Angrai Laine Laga
Bazm E Rindaan Mein Saagar Khanakne Laga
Maikade Pe Barasne Lagi Mastiyaan
Jab Ghata Gir Ke Chaayi Maza Aa gaya

Be Hijabaana Wo Saamne Aagaye
Aur Jawaani Jawaani Se Takra Gayi
Aankh Unki Laree Yoon Meri Aankh Se
Daikh Kar Ye Laraai Maza Aa gaya

Aankh Mein Thee Hayaa Her Mulaqaat Par
Surkh Aariz Hu'ay Wasl Ki Baat Par

Hello!!  My Name is chef Deena from the popular Adupangarai show in Jaya TV Viewers must have seen me in Zee Tamil shows as well.  My Culinary journey as a trainee to become an Executive Chef is incredible. My experience in the culinary field is for more than fifteen years and my USP is Indian cooking !! Apart from being a TV cookery host, my experience lies mainly with being employed in some of the major star hotels across the country especially the Marriott group.

     Chef Deena Cooks is my English Youtube Channel! Practical, simple recipes are my forte and using minimal easily available ingredients is my hallmark. Rudiments of cooking and baking are taught from scratch and any amateur cook can learn to make exciting dishes by watching my channel!  Also, Cooking traditional foods, Easy cooking Recipes, Healthy Snacks, Indian curries, gravies, Baking and Millions of other homemade treats.
